<% content_for :title, "Our Creations" %>

<div class="row">
  <div class="columns large-12">
    <div class="leader-hero">
      <h2>Curators Creations</h2>
      <p>Curators Creations is all about using beautifully made coffee and
      combining it with other complementary ingredients to bring you
      interesting and great tasting beverages.</p>

      <p>Coffee has long been used as an ingredient in many recipes for cakes,
      chocolates and large cups of caramel flavoured milk.</p>

      <p>Modern specialty coffee shops have moved in the opposite direction,
      using coffee as the primary ingredient and only using water and milk
      as the other components of their recipe.  Different coffees are
      frequently featured at Curators simultaneously to highlight
      differences in taste from coffee to coffee. We also know that roast
      profile, brew method and processing of the coffee cherry, amongst
      other factors, all have a huge impact on how a coffee can taste and
      this can be experienced at most third wave coffee shops.</p>

      <p>We will be using all of our skills and knowledge to explore these more
      delicate and intricate flavours you find in coffee to create flavour
      combinations that will excite, challenge and please.</p>

      <p>Each month we will be featuring a Creation that we have worked on. We
      hope you enjoy them as much a we do.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

