      <h3>July's Creation</h3>
      <h4>"Coffee... but not as you know it" or Sparkling Cascara with Lime.</h4>

      <p>Cascara is the dried fruit of the coffee cherry and can be infused in hot water to make a tasty fruity tea like beverage. It usually ends up being discarded in the rush to get to those aromatic beans but it's AWESOME and most importantly packed with caffeine!</p>

      <p>We've made a super strong Cascara reduction for the Creation, mixed with a splash of lime, sparkling water and served over ice. This one will see us through summer with a bang.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

