    <div class="radius leader-hero">
      <h3>March's Creation</h3>
      <p>This month it's called "Flower Power" and it's a sensory explosion. We are using our house coffee from Union as the base, then it's your choice of Espresso or Americano scented with the aroma of coffee flower oil.</p>

      <p>The flower of the coffee plant gives off a jasmine and milk chocolate scent which complements the floral properties of our house coffee perfectly. Combined it enhances your total coffee experience.</p>

      <p>And did you know that in times past, the scent of the flowering coffee plant was said to drive sailors off the African coast crazy as they could smell it 2 miles out to sea!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

